~ start

do Vfx.fade_in(0.7)
do SwitchRoomEffect.switch_room(GlobalVar.room_manager, load("uid://cuje73oplrwyo").instantiate(), SwitchRoomEffect.RoomLocation.NORTH,GlobalVar.current_room)
set GlobalVar.plot = 2.1
do GlobalVar.current_room.plotcheck()
do Vfx.fade_out(0.7)
# The two go outside to gather the necessary materials, and eventually one of the rocks will show a message about the yttrium: "A chunk came off with some metal streaks in it, maybe it's the yttrium we need."  
